{"tid":2055461,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"被問公務員可否網上發表不同聲音　聶德權稱須注意觀感","createTime":"2020-06-08T03:42:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T05:04:53.000Z","uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a6b52fb0bcc0b247706ede336f38773dab51757f","tid":2055461,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T03:42:57.000Z","msg":"公務員事務局局長聶德權說，作為一個普通市民，言論自由是受到基本法保障，但公務員是要執行政府政策，基於這個身份，公務員某方面的言論和表達自由是受到限制，公務人員的言行要符合身份，不能令人質疑或擔心是否真心支持政府政策，為何可以公然反對政府政策。<br />\n<br />\n聶德權在本台節目《千禧年代》被問到，公務員可否在個人網上社交評台發表不同聲音，他回應說，即使只是在網上朋友之間發表意見，但眾所周知網上評台的傳播性很強，大家要有心理準備網上的私人意見，最終會變成不是私人意見，需要注意有關情況引致的影響、後果和給人的觀感。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1530779-20200608.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1530779-20200608.htm&d=jILigwfPQQ17AL812Qo3KcIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=e945f24c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1530779-20200608.htm&h=738e4a52\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1530779-20200608.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年11月5日 - 署理行政長官張建宗說，公務員須政治中立、不偏不倚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0db7973d6f0421d9cd15a06143d31e57d4c0a1a","tid":2055461,"uid":2054,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T03:46:06.000Z","msg":"共匪官員講觀感<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66cc00ec0b4d33edda70f565a15ffb05a3f2ef2f","tid":2055461,"uid":93986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T03:47:35.000Z","msg":"咁撚多限制<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"016b317d64bd6ca59e3249d567b03a93b45b8b96","tid":2055461,"uid":148355,"like":0,"di